记得在MOD主类初始化方法中 注册写了事件那个类 ,比如

@Mod(modid = "one", name = "One", version = "1.0.0")
public class OneMod {
        @EventHandler
        public void load(FMLInitializationEvent event) {
                MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS.register(new EventContainer());
        }
}
